data.description: This BETTER THAN NEW home offers a spacious and luxurious living space with six bedrooms and three bathrooms. With its open floorplan, this home provides ample room for family gatherings and entertaining guests. An $1,800 Lender Credit is available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costs andpre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender. This credit is in addition toany negotiated seller concession.AND THERE'S MORE...The house is located on a picturesque pond, providing a serene and peaceful setting. The two-car garage offers convenient parking and storage space. Additionally, this home features a separate office/flex space, perfect for those who work from home or need a quiet space to focusThe large loft area adds versatility to the home, serving as an additional living area or playroom.  The owner's suite in this home is exceptionally large, providing a private retreat within the house. The suite includes a spacious bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a luxurious ensuite bathroom. The ensuite bathroom is equipped with modern fixtures and finishes. These elegant details add a touch of sophistication to the space.  KEEP GOING! THIS HOUSE HAS IT ALL! The main living areas of this home feature beautiful LVP (Luxury Vinyl Plank) flooring, which is not only stylish but also durable and easy to maintain. This flooring adds warmth and character to the space, making it feel welcoming and cozy. In addition to the LVP flooring, the bedrooms have brand new carpeting, ensuring comfort and luxury throughout the entire home.  Freshly painted walls create a clean and inviting atmosphere in every room of this house. The neutral color scheme allows for easy customization and personalization, making it easy for new homeowners to make this house their own.  The fenced yard surrounding back yard provides privacy and security, making it an ideal space for outdoor activities and entertaining. The yard offers plenty of room for children and pets to play, as well as space for gardening or creating an outdoor oasis. Come see this home today!
